Virginia Martin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Virginia_Martin 0 Virginia Martin (December 2, 1927 – August 27, 2009) was an American actress and singer known for her work on the Broadway stage and on television. She was nominated for the Tony Award for Best Featured Actress in a Musical in 1963.
